Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm of the wind clears reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always confirming that vital due.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've finally made contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can finally confront Gin and Vodka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Recap}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After finding the murderer of Itakura-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And following up to a lead on the Black Organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got Professor Agasa's help and went to Itakura-san's cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then Vodka called while we were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo. what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You better pick up the phone, Itakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find the phone in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By speaking with him, I learned about\NItokura-san's deal with Vodka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4:00, at the Kenbashi station locker room, locker #0032...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the professor's car ended up with a flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we found a couple...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would take us to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:13.88,Title,,0,0,0,,Contact with the Black Organization\N(Desperation Part){Title}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact with the Black Organization: Desperation Part!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Kenbashi station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it under construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There won't be anything running there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We live very close to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinichi, are we really going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only after I finish up something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't what it is, but could you please not whisper in my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! I told you not to smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. I'll throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't throw it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you have an ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, all of the coins are covered in ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be rich. but this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's be expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since these two are the jewel robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car doesn't belong to this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely that they hijacked someone back in Gunma,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After ditching their old car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real owner of this car isn't a smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:05:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And only keeps coins in there to make\Nit easy to pay at toll booths. {Kaizou Translation: to pay at toll boothes}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't realize this until he had already used if once. but kept\Nusing it because the coins were already covered in ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is, until we got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's stupid, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put the change in there to stop him from smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have other proof that this car doesn't belong to this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he isn't used to left-handed handling, the\Ndriver's side was always to the side of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he was always over the center line,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he looked back, he looked over his left\Nshoulder even though it was harder to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also had difficulty shifting gears with his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then there's the signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used the wipers instead of the turn signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the handling is different on imports,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used that lever on accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you stopped to get us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was strange when you moved near the door on my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of the door near the other lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It all come to me after hearing Officer Yamamura's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you're sitting on the wrong side...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood of the other robber, who\Nhad likely been sitting there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That injured colleague of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be in the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably back there to pass through the checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did they let us in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, robbers would never pick up hitch-hikers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they didn't mind us since they needed to pass checkpoints.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:07:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With an old man and a child aboard, the police\Nwould suspect they were on a family trip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how I realized who they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones who would do such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the jewel robbers on the run, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're too smart for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What can we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old man and boy know about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, where do you think we should\Nget rid of this guy and the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not that Kenbashi station that's under construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one will be there, and the construction\Nworkers won't arrive until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, boy, why didn't you tell\Nthe police back at that checkpoint?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've known all along that we're the jewel robbers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I would have told the police then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would have taken us in for questioning, but\N I can't go because I have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can catch you two anytime I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're tough, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You intrigue me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't be talking like that for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't let you go even when you beg for mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no use, I used a tranquilizer on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tranquilizer!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may want to hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brat! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike that jewelry store, I'm not so easily fooled by imitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the... Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right. Watch out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Anywhere Ball Inflation Belt
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,insects gas into a special rubber to make a soccer ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But due to its elasticity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I set it at its maximum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll become as big as a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm leaving now. Call the police and tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You caught the jewel robbers they're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, could you really be going to meet with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there's a station closer to here than Kenbashi, they\Nwon't cancel the meeting just because the police are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not worried about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you over the Detective Badge later
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, stay away from Kenbashi station!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surround the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, don't let anyone escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.80,Signs,,0,0,0,,Coin Lockers{Sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Itakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Itakura, he's not even here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A check?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's for the same amount we gave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is that program we forced him develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left the program and the money since he was so afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me. It looks like Itakura left the goods and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should still be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Only some drunks and a kid entered the station!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be! Look again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This meeting shouldn't be until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time was changed because Itakura-san couldn't do it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you decided it was best to give him the upper hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the time was decided by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He couldn't open the mail at his house due to a blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I called him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to dispose of him but I did get the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His heart is in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't make it much longer anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know why there's tape on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was to get your fingerprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you couldn't peel it off with your gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lit a cigarette when you didn't\Nsee the person you came to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This saliva will tell him your blood type, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you hold on to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also wanted to find our hideouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, there's a tracking device in this case.{Original Sub: ... tracing device...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a clever fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itakura, that bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't Itakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Extreme climate conditions place stress on the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone with heart issues would never go\Nsomewhere like that during a snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the one I talked to on the phone was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was likely someone he hired...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they screwed up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case... It's been wiped down, but it's still emitting heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he must be hiding nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're getting close, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whar now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess there's nowhere for him to hide around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's always somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I doing, an adult couldn't fit in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's disguise and leave, the police could be on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the guy Itakura hired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always be on guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there's someone investigating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fox as clever as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whar now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I follow them? No, it's too soon.\NThey may be waiting to ambush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what is it they're planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara was there to invent strange drugs,\Nbut Itakura-san was a system engineer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had nothing to do with drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That program he abandoned for the sake of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What... is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, nice job here, Agasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're tired, but we need to take you in for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Chiba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we found something over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Haibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? How did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the professor hadn't come home by morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used the spare Homing Glasses find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little girl, did you find your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then you two go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I passed out due to the lack of oxygen in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a quick nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, you think I'll buy that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just hurry home and forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The professor is alright, he's with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 5:00 yesterday, a man was found\Ndead in his New Baker Hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was the famous C.G.\Ndesigner Itakura Suguru-san, age 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next is..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
